Name: isbntools
Version: 0.7.5
Summary: Extract, clean and transform ISBNs (International Standard Book Number).
Home-page: https://github.com/xlcnd/isbntools
Author: Alexandre Conde
Author-email: alexandreconde@hotmail.com
